<main class="tdbc-container">
  <!-- Table for Non-Topics Pages -->
  <div class="tdbc-section">
    <ul class="tdbc-column-container">
      {%- for page in collections.pages -%}
      <li class="tdbc-card">
        <div class="tdbc-card__content">
          <a href="{{ page.url }}" class="tdbc-card__title">{{ page.data.title }}</a>
          <p>{{ page.data.description }}</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>
  </div>

# **🚀 Welcome to The Don’t Panic Protocol**  

## 🔒 **Your Guide to Stress-Free Cybersecurity**  

Welcome to **The Don’t Panic Protocol**, your go-to resource for mastering the art of cybersecurity without the stress. 🌐 In a world filled with online threats, it’s easy to feel overwhelmed—but protecting yourself doesn’t have to be complicated.  

This site is all about making cybersecurity simple, accessible, and actionable for everyone, whether you’re a total beginner or looking to sharpen your digital defenses. Ready to take control of your digital safety? Let’s get started!  

---

## **📋 What Is the Don’t Panic Protocol?**  

The Don’t Panic Protocol is a comprehensive framework designed to help you protect your online life with ease. From securing personal devices to safeguarding your home network, this site provides:  

- **Step-by-step guides** for every aspect of digital security.  
- **Checklists** to track your progress and ensure you’re covering all bases.  
- **Tools and tips** to simplify tricky concepts like encryption, secure messaging, and IoT safety.  
- **Regular updates** to keep you informed about emerging threats and solutions.  

No matter your starting point, we’ll help you take actionable steps to make your digital world safer—without feeling overwhelmed.  

---

## **🔗 Explore the Protocol**  

Cybersecurity covers a lot of ground, so we’ve broken it into focused sections. Click below to explore each topic:  

- 🔐 [Authentication](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/authentication)  
Learn how to strengthen your digital locks with secure passwords, multifactor authentication, and password managers.  
- 🌐 [Web Browsing](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/web-browsing)  
Browse the internet safely with privacy-focused tools, ad blockers, and secure browser settings.  
- 🔄 [Ongoing Maintenance](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/ongoing-maintenance)  
Keep your defenses strong with regular updates, backups, and monitoring for unusual activity.  
- 🌐 [Networks](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/networks)  
Protect your home network with strong router settings, guest networks, and VPNs.  
- 🌐 [Internet of Things (IoT)](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/iot)  
Secure smart devices like cameras, doorbells, and thermostats to keep hackers out of your home.  
- 📱 [Personal Devices](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/personal-devices)  
Protect your smartphones, laptops, and tablets with encryption, antivirus tools, and safe app practices.  
- 🔒 [Physical Security](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/physical-security)  
Combine physical and digital security to safeguard your devices and workspaces.  
- 📩 [Secure Messaging](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/secure-messaging)  
Ensure private conversations with encrypted messaging apps and disappearing messages.  
- 📣 [Social Media](https://dontpanicprotocol.org/social-media)  
Control your digital footprint by adjusting privacy settings and sharing wisely.  

---

## **💡 Why It Matters**  

Cybersecurity isn’t just for techies—it’s for everyone. From protecting your personal information to staying safe on social media, these practices empower you to navigate the online world with confidence.  

Whether it’s avoiding phishing scams, securing your home network, or keeping your messages private, The Don’t Panic Protocol is here to guide you every step of the way.  

